ort curriculum vitae and a list of my published works both of which you may use at your discretion.

I hope you will let me have two copies of your pamphlet,3 one for me, the other for Doubleday.

Wishing you success in this struggle for a just cause,





Sincerely yours,





TO: KATHARINE A. WHITE

CC, 1 p.





Goldwin Smith Hall

Cornell, Ithaca, NY.

February 16, 1957

